---
title: Chicken, Mushroom & Char Siu Udon Noodle Broth with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: If you need any way to change up a chicken and udon noodle broth, you can’t go wrong with a coating of char siu. The
chicken is instantly wrapped in rich flavours and combined with the seasoned broth for a bowl that is purely delicious.
